description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Regional Leads, Venture-People&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;(Surrey, Herts and Essex) &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Named Community Provider of the Year for the last two years, Venture-People work with people where they are. We have a proven approach for supporting people with complex mental health needs and are now ready to replicate this in other counties and are now looking for Regional Leaders based in Surrey, Hertfordshire and Essex who want to make a real difference to the lives of people with complex mental health needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;trained in Psychology, Social Work or Nursing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;experienced in dealing with patients directly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;able to make hard decisions and justify them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;articulate, both verbally and in writing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;motivated to provide high quality services to individuals with a complex and/or forensic risk profile&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;frustrated by bureaucracy and red tape!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You believe…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;in recovery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;in always delivering on promises you make&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;in taking personal responsibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;in creative solutions to difficult problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;in finding better ways to do things&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;you can change the world!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You want…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;to grow and lead your own team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;to make things happen&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;to inspire and be inspired&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;to be part of a dynamic business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;to be encouraged to innovate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;to find the angle that turns a ‘No’ into a ‘Yes’!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If the above describes you, please contact rebecca.pacy@venture-people.com for a life changing conversation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for the right people to start as soon as possible and the role will be subject to a satisfactory DBS check and you will need a full driving licence and access to a car.&lt;/p&gt;
